SnapshotOraclev11g.name: VM_MUNICIPIO
SnapshotOraclev11g.subquery:
SELECT MUNICIPIO.IBGE AS ID_MUNICIPIO ,
MUNICIPIO."NOME DO MUNICIPIO" AS MUNICIPIO,
MUNICIPIO.UF AS UF,
MUNICIPIO."CODIGO NACIONAL" AS AREA
FROM VW_MAPVIEW_MUNICIPIO municipio
WHERE municipio.ibge IN
(SELECT UNIQUE(IBGE) FROM VW_MAPVIEW_ESTACAO_LOCATION
)
